    <!-- Device Admin & Accessibility -->
    <string name="accessibility_service_description">Suzy Snooze uses Accessibility Service to detect when the phone screen is locked/unlocked to automatically restore your ringer and notification volume after snooze ends. No information is collected, transmitted, or stored off-device. All data (snooze schedule, volume settings, optional alarm labels) is stored locally on your device only. Optional alarm labels may be spoken using your device\'s native text-to-speech.</string>
    <string name="device_admin_description">Suzy Snooze uses Device Administrator permission to manage Do Not Disturb mode and set ringer to silent during snooze. When snooze ends, volume is restored to 80%. No information is collected, transmitted, or stored off-device. All settings are stored locally on your device only.</string>
